        "timestamp": "2020-05-04 00:28:00.000000000",
        "message": "Patch Set 1:\n\nThis should tell spring to use the constructor annotated with Autowired\n\n\"As of Spring Framework 4.3, an @Autowired annotation on such a constructor is no longer necessary if the target bean only defines one constructor to begin with. However, if several constructors are available, at least one must be annotated to teach the container which one to use\"\n\nReference : https://docs.spring.io/spring/docs/4.3.x/spring-framework-reference/htmlsingle/#beans-autowired-annotation",
        "patchset_number": 1
      },
